Sterling Grove - The Providence Collection in Surprise, Arizona, features award-winning home designs ranging from 1,529 to 2,505 square feet with distinct farmhouse, craftsman, prairie, and Spanish architecture. Centered around a tree-lined town square, the master plan community features lush cornerstone parks, gardens and groves, beautiful water features, and miles of walking trails throughout. Virtually tour and explore the Smithfield home design on TollBrothers.com/AZ. 
#LoveEverythingAboutHome

node.text:
Served by the North Clackamas School District, Toll Brothers at Scouters Mountain is a premier community offering luxurious 2- and 3-story homes ranging from 4 to 5 bedrooms and 2,345 to 3,669 square feet. Sophisticated finishes and innovative features make these stately homes ideal for those looking to live in the desirable Happy Valley area. Residents will enjoy living in close proximity to excellent schools, a vast variety of shopping and dining options, and abundant recreation opportunities, including nearby walking trails. For more varied entertainment, Portland’s vibrant downtown is only 15 miles away. Virtually tour and explore the Gearhart home design in beautiful Oregon on TollBrothers.com/OR. 
#LoveEverythingAboutHome
